								<li data-translate="course.highlights.ai">✅ AI-powered platform training</li>
								<li data-translate="course.highlights.mixed">✅ Mix of online and offline sessions</li>
								<li data-translate="course.highlights.georgian">✅ Georgian market focus</li>
								<li data-translate="course.highlights.practical">✅ Practical business applications</li>
